PrecisRe-appointment of JEAN-CHARLES CLOUTIER, of Limoges, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Public Service Staff Relations Board to hold office during good behaviour for a period of three years; and order that JEAN-CHARLES CLOUTIER shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act, effective April 28, 1999.
Attachments
precis:
Re-appointment of JEAN-CHARLES CLOUTIER, of Limoges, Ontario, as a
full-time member of the Public Service Staff Relations Board to hold
office during good behaviour for a period of three years; and order that
JEAN-CHARLES CLOUTIER shall be deemed to be employed in the Public
Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act,
effective April 28, 1999.
